==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wishbone
<hw>Wish"bone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The forked bone in
front of the breastbone in birds; -- called also
<altname>merrythought</altname>, and <altname>wishing bone</altname>.
See <er>Merrythought</er>, and <er>Furculum</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wishedly</ent>⟦br⟧
